The MIT grant above covers the Python re-implementation authored in this
repository (palustris_me.py, the test/validation code, and documentation).

Third-party material, NOT covered by the MIT grant above:

  data/ and validation/gams_reference/ are the original R. palustris ME-model
  of Chowdhury, Alsiyabi & Saha (Microbiology Spectrum 2022,
  doi:10.1128/spectrum.01463-22; source: github.com/ssbio/palustris_ME_model).

  As of July 2026 the upstream repository carries NO license file, so its authors
  have not formally granted rights to copy, modify, or redistribute these files.
  They remain the work of the Saha lab and are included here in good faith, for
  scientific reproducibility, with full citation of the paper above. GitHub's
  Terms of Service (D.4) allow other GitHub users to view and fork this repository;
  beyond that, if you wish to redistribute or build on the Saha-lab files, please
  cite the paper and contact the original authors for explicit permission.
